proposal:
Greetings to the sun-powered community of STA! 🌞

It's no secret that you guys are lighting up the world with your solar technologies, and we're here to help you shine even brighter. We're not in the business of selling solar panels, but we do have some tools that could help your community grow and thrive. 

1. 🔄 DEX (UNI FACTORY): Create your own DEX based on Uniswap V2 and set your commission from 0.00% to 20%. Customize it to match your brand's colors, logo, and menus. The price? A revenue share model so you don't have to pay upfront.

2. 🎰 Lottery: Ever thought about running a blockchain-based lottery? You can earn a commission of 0-30%. It's supported on ETH, BSC, and Polygon blockchains and supports ERC20 (BEP20) tokens.

3. 🪙 Wallet: Create a multicurrency crypto wallet for just $999. It supports Bitcoin, Ethereum, and tokens with features like P2P exchange via atomic swaps, customizing tokens, setting commissions, and Visa/MC integration.

4. 🌾 Farming: Attract investment by offering rewards with ERC20 Staking & Yield Farming. The price is just $799 and you can use any ERC20 tokens, including Uniswap lp.

5. 🗳 DAO: For $600, you can have governance and proposals for your crypto token where stakeholders can create/vote for proposals without spending on gas.

6. 🌉 CrossChain: Create an EVM compatible blockchain bridge for $1500. It's based on multichain.org's open sources and all EVM blockchains can be supported.

7. 🚀 IDOFactory - Launchpad: Launchpad solution for IDO pools and token locking for $950. Use your token for IDO pools or native coins like ETH, BNB for token lockers.

These tools are all B2B, so you're not playing, you're creating. And with 21Cr STA tokens in circulation, there's plenty of opportunity for growth! Plus, with a community of more than 30,000 farmers & customers, we're sure there's a lot of potential for these tools to thrive.

Interested in taking your project to the next level? Check out https://t.me/onoutdemos for more information. Remember, the sun never sets on the blockchain. ☀️🚀

Let me know if you're interested! 👋
